    {
      "comment": {
        "id": "99e7a30e-2aa7-4b0a-8a44-519b5f6b882c",
        "created_at": "2025-05-24T00:48:46.413Z",
        "updated_at": "2025-05-26T23:02:21.307Z",
        "post_id": "cc4a0c58-0784-4f9a-b331-1edc3eedf590",
        "user_id": 25847676,
        "body": "Even though she likely won’t see this for quite a few days, I wanted to offer my thanks to Alma for making me a better options trader.  Eleven days ago, she first mentioned that the odds were looking pretty good for a mean-reverting trade (but it should be hedged).  So I started building a hedged position and slowly added to it over the last two weeks.  Today, I rolled it down to take advantage of the new spot levels.  My profits (including the loss on the hedge) were 69+%.  The “old” me wouldn’t have hedged, and wouldn’t have rolled it down to lock in some of the profits.  So thank you!!!",
        "status": "published",
        "parent_id": null,
        "is_locked": false,
        "quote_id": null,
        "pub_moderation_status": null,
        "trust_and_safety_status": null,
        "media_uploads": null,
        "reaction_count": 7,
        "reply_count": 0,
        "max_reply_created_at": null,
