        "has_reacted": false,
        "reactions": {
          "thumbs_up": 3,
          "upvote": 4
        },
        "muted": true,
        "reported_by_user": false,
        "raw_body": "Even though she likely won’t see this for quite a few days, I wanted to offer my thanks to Alma for making me a better options trader.  Eleven days ago, she first mentioned that the odds were looking pretty good for a mean-reverting trade (but it should be hedged).  So I started building a hedged position and slowly added to it over the last two weeks.  Today, I rolled it down to take advantage of the new spot levels.  My profits (including the loss on the hedge) were 69+%.  The “old” me wouldn’t have hedged, and wouldn’t have rolled it down to lock in some of the profits.  So thank you!!!",
        "user_pub_role": null,
        "most_recent_comment_created_at": null,
        "mediaAttachments": []
      },
